The prison officials have evacuated about six bodies of those who died in the attack on the Kuje Correctional Services Centre by dare-devil terrorists in Abuja.SaharaReporters at the scene of the attack counted six bodies that were dumped on the floor of the premises of the building and covered with blankets.





